## CWTools 配置 — MC-Mini MOD
## 放在 MC-Mini/ 根目录下

## 声明 MOD 类型和游戏路径
cwtools HOI4

## 声明 MOD 额外文件目录（CWTools 会扫描这些目录里的自定义内容）
## 这样就不会把自定义 idea/event/focus 标红
config = {
    common/ideas/**
    common/bop/**
    common/countries/**
    common/characters/**
    common/decisions/**
    common/decisions/categories/**
    common/ideologies/**
    common/names/**
    common/national_focus/**
    common/country_tags/**
    common/equipment/**
    common/country_leader/**
    events/**
    history/**
    history/countries/**
    history/states/**
    history/units/**
    localisation/**
    localisation/simp_chinese/**
    music/**
    interface/**
    gfx/**
    map/**
}
